{"tid":1632613,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"如果熱門仲係冇和理非活動，我宣佈正式完結","createTime":"2019-10-06T18:57:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T20:09:30.000Z","uid":140302,"like":25,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"9d7c20dbb5f358f14783afee29e3412e971a2233","tid":1632613,"uid":140302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:57:02.000Z","msg":"我屌你老母你哋係咪冇睇過winter on fire<br />\n<br />\n和理非 &gt;勇武 &gt;和理非 &gt;勇武 &gt;和理非 &gt;勇武  loop到成功<br />\n<br />\n個班人定係鬼定係走火入魔<br />\n定係呢排連登風向非常奇怪令到大家都要咁，<br />\n大家其實一早有共識我哋要做嘅係乜嘢<br />\n上面嗰條成功方程式<br />\n<br />\n再加<br />\n<br />\n唔割席 唔分化<br />\n<br />\n而家根本係風向鼓吹勇武不斷升級唔俾文宣同埋和理非入場時間<br />\n<br />\n屌我分化嘅，唔該你諗下今日係咪有一個post 唔熄燈擺明吹鳩你風向，好快成個post跌咗落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a613a694199c04cfabe13f651069609de93099b0","tid":1632613,"uid":140302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:58:08.000Z","msg":"推10下冇人理我收皮"},{"pid":"c6e1f58743cf2285850fd7da4982c5b199710491","tid":1632613,"uid":140302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:58:19.000Z","msg":"推10下冇人理我收皮"},{"pid":"06305a554bd8ec15a50ae64112c80c2f99990142","tid":1632613,"uid":181581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:58:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"24df18313cabe5ae4f44b31e34f9104c21c0b002","tid":1632613,"uid":140302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:59:18.000Z","msg":"推10下冇人理我收皮"},{"pid":"4bdbe0d65cb904e6d33cdc1fc8b88041b7a37f7c","tid":1632613,"uid":140302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:59:38.000Z","msg":"推10下冇人理我收皮"},{"pid":"308cc9a476f2efb8d04810ef6d7bfd4e20f6f33f","tid":1632613,"uid":143151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:59:43.000Z","msg":"推俾外國旅客 咪俾黨鐵賺錢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1632118\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/16